{"tid":982253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［估省份］超市開張玩呢招瀨嘢！ 幾分鐘即嚇到閂門","createTime":"2019-01-15T03:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T04:37:36.000Z","uid":176442,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"565df20444255d450eb321c3cf34aaad62dc0ef8","tid":982253,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190115&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59141491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190115%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59141491&d=7Q0TnbiuGBwu1kYG%2F7S3uiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=792b8014\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190115%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59141491&h=3c1ee1e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190115&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59141491</a><br />\n<br />\n【新增動新聞】江蘇高郵一間超市本月11日開張，為了吸引客人，超市事先張揚，只要去辦會員卡，便可獲贈6粒雞蛋。結果吸引了大批大媽大叔一早7時就來排隊，把超市門口擠得水洩不通。店方更因為人實在太多，才開門幾分鐘，就隨即落閘了！<br />\n<br />\n有老人表示，當天早上7時就在店外排隊等拿免費雞蛋。有人稱，超市開業前派傳單，要人去辦會員卡，免費領取雞蛋。不過，一名大媽來排隊後卻兩樣皆失，憤怒地說：「今天又不辦卡，憑單張（傳單）也拿不到，甚麼用都沒有，白白排隊！」就算是拿到免費雞蛋的大叔，亦同樣憤怒。他說：「首先態度不好，開甚麼超市。」　<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a32da981e30e177d773c8bce99acb9fffb6821","tid":982253,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老味D人多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e114e9f35f518cce269ebe4fa7be0b079d4b1599","tid":982253,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190114/large/1547481344_6b3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190114%2Flarge%2F1547481344_6b3c.jpg&h=761547f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n磁能線<br />\n排隊排到出宇宙都得"},{"pid":"2e2163483667db83a7efbd53d4a0224c355c28e9","tid":982253,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"6粒雞蛋 ..."},{"pid":"8b7084f5b5f6786edc12624dfe32a9d113745fbb","tid":982253,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:12:29.000Z","msg":"笑𨶙死"},{"pid":"53abe84eb4043b988116ace1d500a27b2b75ad5b","tid":982253,"uid":48162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"其實轉個頭拎曬啲資料去賣都fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2788625de38b43086f3b153a54620e699a9ed01f","tid":982253,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:19:36.000Z","msg":"一開張就關門大吉"},{"pid":"d773ae5e35cbebc183f6ddee147014280aa8e5e0","tid":982253,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"香港有90s 00s排喜茶"},{"pid":"af5e4066a0a2d40432662f6eb9a750c915215f7a","tid":982253,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"6隻蛋成本比到盡咪3蚊"},{"pid":"d49d230c0968fc85573cdd6a2f7e78f90a28f674","tid":982253,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53abe84eb4043b988116ace1d500a27b2b75ad5b","tid":982253,"uid":48162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"其實轉個頭拎曬啲資料去賣都fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾級別嘅資料冇用，佢哋自己都咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01665ecda3fb617166f804973d17995120a7363","tid":982253,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"其實咁幾好,咁少成本就可以吸引咁大人流,做生意實冇死"},{"pid":"dbb6007622611f64bf66b401d8f4e5bc1624a768","tid":982253,"uid":74361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc